highlights.text: “Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 193 weeks straight.
“Despeinada” by Ozuna and Camilo is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 80 spots at #91.
“OK Not To Be OK” by Marshmello and Demi Lovato is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #56.
Juice WRLD has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Come & Go (with Marshmello)” is the highest at #24.
